{"tid":1979580,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"政府今年將增聘過萬名公務員，連登手足一齊報名，應承我一齊體制內抗爭好唔好！！！","createTime":"2020-04-19T13:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T13:59:17.000Z","uid":118346,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"23caa57c69d85676ffd6970a2758d6850f0d1b37","tid":1979580,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗感謝立法會財委會通過第二輪防疫抗疫基金，會盡早落實措施，保障市民就業。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗在網誌表示受疫情影響，預計星期一公布的第一季失業率會比現時的3.7%進一步上升，短期內亦難以好轉，當中應屆畢業生就業將比往年困難。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指，除推行保就業計劃外，政府亦計劃增聘超過一萬名公務員，歡迎有理想、有承擔、有國家觀念、香港情懷、視香港為家的年輕人加入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=388193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388193&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=dde2623e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388193&h=cf721da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=388193</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3da9286729840e60bd646d58e230563fac7fe4","tid":1979580,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"狗佔幾多"}]}